OL,3,CBritish army could be 'expended'
OL,4,Cwithin six months in major war,
OL,5,Cminister says
OL,7,FThe British army could be "expended"
OL,8,Fwithin six months if faced with a war
OL,9,Fon a similar to scale to that in
OL,10,FUkraine, a defence minister has warned.
OL,12,FIn a speech on Wednesday, Alistair
OL,13,FCarns, a former Royal Marines colonel,
OL,14,Fstressed the need to "generate depth
OL,15,Fand mass rapidly in the event of a
OL,16,Fcrisis".
