OL,3,CBritish army could be 'expended'
OL,4,Cwithin six months in major war,
OL,5,Cminister says
OL,7,F"In a war of scale ` not a limited
OL,8,Fintervention, but one similar to
OL,9,FUkraine ` our army for example, on the
OL,10,Fcurrent casualty rates, would be
OL,11,Fexpended ` as part of a broader
OL,12,Fmultinational coalition ` in six
OL,13,Fmonths to a year," Mr Carns said at
OL,14,Fthe Royal United Services Institute
OL,15,F(Rusi) defence think tank in London.
OL,17,FHe added: "That doesn't mean we need a
OL,18,Fbigger army, but it does mean you need
OL,19,Fto generate depth and mass rapidly in
OL,20,Fthe event of a crisis."
