OL,3,CBritish army could be 'expended'
OL,4,Cwithin six months in major war,
OL,5,Cminister says
OL,7,FOfficial figures show the army had
OL,8,F109,245 personnel on October 1,
OL,9,Fincluding 25,814 volunteer reservists.
OL,11,FMr Carns, who is also the minister for
OL,12,Fveterans and people, said the UK
OL,13,Fneeded to "catch up with Nato allies"
OL,14,Fto place greater emphasis on the
OL,15,Freserves.
OL,17,FHowever, the head of the armed forces,
OL,18,FAdmiral Sir Tony Radakin, cast doubt
OL,19,Fon the possibility.
