OL,3,CBritish army could be 'expended'
OL,4,Cwithin six months in major war,
OL,5,Cminister says
OL,7,FAlso speaking at Rusi, the Chief of
OL,8,Fthe Defence Staff said the UK's
OL,9,Fnuclear arsenal is "the one part of
OL,10,Four inventory of which Russia is most
OL,11,Faware and has more impact on
OL,12,F(President Vladimir) Putin than
OL,13,Fanything else".
OL,15,FSuccessive British governments had
OL,16,Finvested "substantial sums of money"
OL,17,Fin renewing nuclear submarines and
OL,18,Fwarheads because of this, he added.
