OL,3,CBritish army could be 'expended'
OL,4,Cwithin six months in major war,
OL,5,Cminister says
OL,7,FSir Tony added that Britain needed to
OL,8,Fbe "clear-eyed in our assessment" of
OL,9,Fthe threats it faces.
OL,11,F"That includes recognising that there
OL,12,Fis only a remote chance of a
OL,13,Fsignificant direct attack or invasion
OL,14,Fby Russia on the United Kingdom, and
OL,15,Fthat's the same for the whole of
OL,16,FNato," he added.
OL,18,FMoscow "knows the response will be
OL,19,Foverwhelming", he added, but warned
OL,20,Fthe nuclear deterrent needed to be
OL,21,F"kept strong and strengthened".
