OL,7,FSir Tony added: "We are at the dawn of
OL,8,Fa third nuclear age, which is
OL,9,Faltogether more complex. It is defined
OL,10,Fby multiple and concurrent dilemmas,
OL,11,Fproliferating nuclear and disruptive
OL,12,Ftechnologies and the almost total
OL,13,Fabsence of the security architectures
OL,14,Fthat went before."
OL,16,FThe first nuclear age was the Cold
OL,17,FWar, while the second was "governed by
OL,18,Fdisarmament efforts and counter
OL,19,Fproliferation", the armed forces chief
OL,20,Fadded.
