OL,7,FHe listed the "wild threats of
OL,8,Ftactical nuclear use" by Russia, China
OL,9,Fbuilding up its weapon stocks, Iran's
OL,10,Ffailure to co-operate with a nuclear
OL,11,Fdeal, and North Korea's "erratic
OL,12,Fbehaviour" among the threats faced by
OL,13,Fthe West.
OL,15,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,16,Fspokesman said Defence Secretary John
OL,17,FHealey had previously spoken about
OL,18,F"the state of the armed forces that
OL,19,Fwere inherited from the previous
OL,20,Fgovernment".
